{"tid":941573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老貓：咬老綜成最大贏家】綜援金加2.8%通過　議員指增幅小轟政府孤寒","createTime":"2018-12-15T02:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T04:22:53.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e1f04a5f34421fdf15840b0af46b989816749370","tid":941573,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"綜援金加2.8%通過　議員指增幅小轟政府孤寒<br />\n<br />\n立法會財務委員會今日(14日)通過明年2月起，將綜援和公共福利金金額上調2.8%，涉及分別4.09億港元和21.54億港元的撥款。勞工及福利局副局長徐英偉指，加幅是按機制訂定，又強調當局無計劃全面檢討綜援制度。<br />\n<br />\n根據當局訂定的加幅，普通及高額長者生活津貼每月分別增加75港元和100港元，而生果金則增加40港元，所有措施預計每年額外增加12.5億港元財政開支。多名議員炮轟金額增幅小，指政府「孤寒」及令綜援人士感到生活沒有尊嚴。議員張超雄指，政府的貧窮政策介入後，墮入貧窮線的貧窮人口反而愈來愈多，批評「每日加幾蚊」是無助脫貧，炮轟當局不願全面檢討綜援制度。<br />\n<br />\n徐英偉重申，有現行機制計算相關加幅，又指貧窮線是一項比較工具，總會有人跌落去，而綜援個案數目已持續下跌至平穩水平。他又提到，不少長者在65歲退休後，因失去收入而跌落貧窮線，惟長者仍有物業等資產，當局會優化不同政策提供協助。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181214/mobile/bkn-20181214193003091-1214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181214%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181214193003091-1214_00822_001.html&d=K%2FtronHRi6BLACeVraY2JLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7bae43c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181214/mobile/bkn-20181214193003091-1214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"baf6493bcb6a7c3d8e70f1cd12ccb3f571286fbe","tid":941573,"uid":30788,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:13:47.000Z","msg":"加咁少點去旅行"},{"pid":"72f23b974a6c4cf0b2f2cfe2e2edd50462a20f93","tid":941573,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"追唔上iphone加幅。。。綜援就冇得換電話冇人權？"},{"pid":"4e95ab03c435ccbf4bd9d4681f5be285851d13d7","tid":941573,"uid":169579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:32:21.000Z","msg":"指政府「孤寒」及令綜援人士感到生活沒有尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n拎綜援又點談尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過生果金加得太少就真嘅"},{"pid":"662815023dd6f0b46d1cebe4bb5b07a6c3927534","tid":941573,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"啲錢都唔夠買層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6ce7e9b49bd11f69230f06190131c7e98b869b","tid":941573,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"正苦戇尻尻 班有物業既老野都係自住 唔通冇錢開飯賣左個物業呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  綜援個班就真係唔應該加啦 cut尻曬去就差唔多 要有尊嚴就自己去打工搵錢而唔係要全香港人養你班綜援垃圾囉"},{"pid":"db7f64ebc1ed8b2b77fbf65f9443141b6db5ebb2","tid":941573,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:58:57.000Z","msg":"班撚屌仲有尊嚴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a13989b32a279e7527d67212ee34cf4c9c81cf","tid":941573,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c90da31a29cc14851b0ec16338ea98c145668a84","tid":941573,"uid":138713,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:05:21.000Z","msg":"根本要Cut撚左綜援啦!!<br />\n養住班廢人!!"},{"pid":"33e52e994447306b4ecb3a2399b752aef8f29c19","tid":941573,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"乞錢都有得嫌少，咩世界"},{"pid":"c8c33ef756144ea9134108cf17da4ca80e076399","tid":941573,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:26:04.000Z","msg":"大種乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嫌錢少咪唔好撚攞"},{"pid":"984bcc2681be6eb9944b70193f1ba71d6b1b99ef","tid":941573,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"綜援好過打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7d37ba02e35e3a192bab2142dc8921a6e197a8","tid":941573,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/